---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Liebherr Wine Cooler Repair | Southern California | HW + WU + WS German";
const description = "Liebherr wine cooler repair Southern California — HWgb / WU / WS single + dual + tri-zone German specialty. Kirchdorf Germany 1949 family. $89 diagnostic. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/liebherr-wine-cooler-repair/";

const faqs = [
  { q: "Which Liebherr wine cooler models are common in LA luxury kitchens?", a: "Liebherr's wine storage line centers on three platforms: <b>HWgb integrated column</b> (panel-ready built-in wine storage with Liebherr's full-overlay European integration standard); <b>WU undercounter</b> (24-inch undercounter-format wine cooler for kitchen islands + butler's pantries + bar zones); <b>WS freestanding</b> (full-size freestanding wine storage). Single-zone, dual-zone, and tri-zone architectures available across the range. LA install concentration: West Hollywood + Silver Lake + Los Feliz design-forward European kitchens, Beverly Hills + Brentwood luxury remodels, Pacific Palisades + Malibu architectural custom, Pasadena + Montecito established luxury. Liebherr's refrigeration-specialist engineering (Liebherr-Hausgeräte GmbH is a dedicated subsidiary of Liebherr Group, focused entirely on refrigeration rather than broader appliance portfolios) translates to long-service-life wine storage with 15+ year design life expectation." },
  { q: "Liebherr wine cooler temperature drift or zone imbalance — diagnostic?", a: "Standard Liebherr wine cooler diagnostic: (1) condenser clean $120–$180 (front-mount condenser dust accumulation first); (2) door gasket compression check — European-spec seal profile at 10-15 yr compression loss causes warm-air infiltration; $300–$440 per section; (3) temperature sensor NTC per zone $260–$340 — drift at 5-8 year mark; (4) evaporator fan motor per zone $320–$480 — tri-zone units have individual fans per zone; (5) dual/tri-zone damper mechanism $280–$420 on zone-separated airflow architectures; (6) compressor start relay + capacitor $280–$400; (7) compressor replacement $900–$1,450. Liebherr's refrigeration-specialist engineering means components are typically robust — rebuild economics strongly favor repair vs replacement at 10-15 years." },
  { q: "Tri-zone Liebherr wine cooler — what's different about service?", a: "Liebherr's tri-zone wine coolers maintain three distinct temperature zones for red / white / champagne storage at different set temperatures. Service implications: (1) each zone has its own NTC temperature sensor + evaporator fan + control logic — differential zone failure is common (two zones working, one drifted); (2) zone damper mechanisms control airflow separation — stuck damper causes one zone to drift toward adjacent zone's temperature; (3) control board logic on tri-zone units is more complex than single/dual zone — board-level diagnostic requires specific Liebherr test sequences; (4) compressor serves all three zones via zone-specific evaporator coils — compressor failure affects all zones simultaneously (distinguishes from zone-specific failures). Tri-zone service typical 10-20% higher than dual-zone given component count; zone-specific repairs can often isolate to the affected zone without touching working zones." },
  { q: "What does Liebherr wine cooler repair cost in LA?", a: "Residential diagnostic $89 waived with repair. Common Liebherr wine cooler bands: condenser clean $120–$180; NTC sensor $260–$340 per zone; evaporator fan motor $320–$480 per zone; door gasket $300–$440 per section; zone damper mechanism $280–$420; compressor start relay + capacitor $280–$400; compressor replacement $900–$1,450 including refrigerant recharge; main control board $460–$680; display board $340–$500; panel-overlay gasket (HWgb integrated) $340–$480; comprehensive refresh package $800–$1,200. Liebherr service runs at upper-European-luxury tier comparable to Miele; parts lead 5-10 days typical via Liebherr USA distribution on common components, 2-3 week on specialty integration hardware or tri-zone specific OEM." },
  { q: "Does Liebherr build walk-in wine cellar cooling systems?", a: "Liebherr's primary US-market focus is appliance-scale wine coolers (this page scope). Liebherr does manufacture commercial-grade wine cellar cooling systems in European markets, but the US distribution emphasizes residential wine cooler / undercounter / built-in column product. For walk-in wine cellar cooling (room-scale 500-10,000+ bottle systems), the dominant US brands are WhisperKool, Wine Guardian, CellarPro, Breezaire, and Vinotheque — see our <a href='/services/wine-cellar-repair/'>wine cellar service hub</a> for walk-in scope. Our Liebherr service on this page covers the residential wine cooler product line specifically; walk-in cellar cooling brands are separate service scope." },
  { q: "Liebherr wine cooler vs Sub-Zero vs Miele — practical service comparison?", a: "All three are luxury wine cooler brands with strong LA install bases but distinct service characteristics. <b>Liebherr</b> (this page) — refrigeration specialist, German engineering, 15+ year design life, parts via Liebherr USA 5-10 day typical. <b>Sub-Zero</b> — dual compressor architecture, integrated column panel-ready, Sub-Zero Group matched suite context, parts via Madison WI 3-5 day. <b>Miele</b> — MasterCool integration, Miele@home Wi-Fi, family-ownership engineering continuity, parts via Miele USA + Alabama 2025 plant. Choice driver: Liebherr for refrigeration-specialist engineering + tri-zone flexibility; Sub-Zero for Sub-Zero Group suite integration + dual compressor; Miele for MasterCool suite + Miele@home + European integration standard. Service economics similar across all three at upper-luxury tier. See <a href='/brands/sub-zero-wine-cooler-repair/'>Sub-Zero wine cooler</a> + <a href='/brands/miele-wine-cooler-repair/'>Miele wine cooler</a>." }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair — Liebherr Wine Cooler Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical, "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL, "priceRange": "$$$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "Liebherr Wine Cooler Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "Liebherr wine cooler repair across Southern California — LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, Riverside. HWgb integrated column + WU 24\" undercounter + WS freestanding. Single, dual, and tri-zone wine storage. Kirchdorf an der Iller Germany family since 1949; refrigeration-specialist engineering. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } })) },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Liebherr", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/liebherr-refrigerator-repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Liebherr Wine Cooler Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">{schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}</Fragment>
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Liebherr wine cooler service? Same-day across all 5 SoCal counties:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › <a href="/brands/liebherr-refrigerator-repair/">Liebherr</a> › Wine Cooler Repair</div>
    <h1>Liebherr Wine Cooler Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Liebherr is the refrigeration specialist of luxury wine storage — Liebherr-Hausgeräte GmbH (subsidiary of the broader Liebherr Group founded 1949 by Hans Liebherr in Kirchdorf an der Iller, Germany) concentrates engineering specifically on refrigeration + freezing technology rather than broader appliance portfolios. Wine cooler lineup: <b>HWgb integrated column</b> panel-ready built-in; <b>WU 24-inch undercounter</b>; <b>WS freestanding</b> full-size wine storage; single-zone, dual-zone, and tri-zone architectures across the range. 15+ year design life expectation reflects refrigeration-specialist engineering focus. LA install concentration: West Hollywood + Silver Lake + Los Feliz design-forward European kitchens, Beverly Hills + Brentwood luxury remodels, Pacific Palisades + Malibu architectural custom, Pasadena + Montecito established luxury. Parts via Liebherr USA distribution typical 5-10 day LA-authorized service lead. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
    <ul class="hero-facts">
      <li><b>HWgb + WU + WS</b> — integrated column + undercounter + freestanding</li>
      <li><b>Single + dual + tri-zone</b> — red/white/champagne temperature flexibility</li>
      <li><b>Kirchdorf Germany 1949</b> — Liebherr family 3 generations</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b> — waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>BHGS #A49573 · Insured</span><span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Common Liebherr wine cooler failures our techs see in LA</h2>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Temperature drift — condenser + gasket + sensor</h3><p>Sequential diagnostic. Condenser clean $120–$180; European-spec gasket $300–$440; NTC sensor $260–$340 per zone.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Tri-zone differential — zone-specific components</h3><p>One zone drifted, others working = zone fan / sensor / damper fault. Fan $320–$480 or damper $280–$420 or sensor $260–$340.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>HWgb integrated panel-overlay service</h3><p>Panel-ready integrated requires finish-protection discipline. Interior work access preferred; panel-overlay gasket $340–$480.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Compressor start — relay-first diagnostic</h3><p>Relay + capacitor $280–$400 before escalating. Most 'not cooling' resolve without compressor work.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Control board on current electronic generations</h3><p>Liebherr digital control $460–$680 main board + $340–$500 display. Less common on older generations.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Vibration — wine collection protection</h3><p>Compressor isolation mount deterioration at 10-15 yr. Mount swap $240–$380 preserves collection-safe vibration spec.</p></div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>What Liebherr wine cooler repair typically costs</h2>
    <table class="price-table">
      <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Waived with repair</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Condenser deep clean</td><td>$120 – $180</td><td>Annual maintenance</td></tr>
      <tr><td>NTC temperature sensor</td><td>$260 – $340</td><td>Per zone</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Evaporator fan motor</td><td>$320 – $480</td><td>Per zone; tri-zone has 3 fans</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Zone damper mechanism</td><td>$280 – $420</td><td>Tri-zone architecture</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door gasket (European spec)</td><td>$300 – $440</td><td>Per section</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Compressor start relay + capacitor</td><td>$280 – $400</td><td>First-line diagnostic</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Compressor replacement</td><td>$900 – $1,450</td><td>Refrigerant recharge included</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Compressor isolation mounts</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>Vibration reduction</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Main control board</td><td>$460 – $680</td><td>Current electronic generations</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Panel-overlay gasket (HWgb integrated)</td><td>$340 – $480</td><td>Full-overlay panel models</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Comprehensive refresh (10-15 yr)</td><td>$800 – $1,200</td><td>Gasket + sensor + clean</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/liebherr-refrigerator-repair/">Liebherr refrigerator</a> · <a href="/brands/liebherr-built-in-refrigerator-repair/">Liebherr built-in</a> · <a href="/services/wine-cooler-repair/">Wine cooler service hub</a> · <a href="/services/wine-cellar-repair/">Wine cellar service hub (walk-in scale)</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Service areas — where our Liebherr wine cooler calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>West Hollywood + design-forward</h4><p><a href="/west-hollywood/">West Hollywood</a> · Silver Lake · Los Feliz</p></div>
      <div><h4>Beverly Hills + Bel Air</h4><p><a href="/beverly-hills/">Beverly Hills</a> · Bel Air</p></div>
      <div><h4>Brentwood + Pacific Palisades</h4><p><a href="/brentwood/">Brentwood</a> · Pacific Palisades</p></div>
      <div><h4>Malibu + coastal</h4><p><a href="/malibu/">Malibu</a> · Manhattan Beach · Palos Verdes</p></div>
      <div><h4>Pasadena + San Marino</h4><p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · San Marino · La Cañada</p></div>
      <div><h4>OC luxury</h4><p>Newport Coast · Corona del Mar · <a href="/irvine/">Irvine</a></p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Related Liebherr + wine cooler pages</h2>
    <ul class="related-links">
      <li><a href="/brands/liebherr-refrigerator-repair/">Liebherr refrigerator (broader) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/liebherr-built-in-refrigerator-repair/">Liebherr built-in refrigerator →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/services/wine-cooler-repair/">Wine cooler service hub →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/services/wine-cellar-repair/">Wine cellar service hub (walk-in) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/sub-zero-wine-cooler-repair/">Sub-Zero wine cooler (luxury alt) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/miele-wine-cooler-repair/">Miele wine cooler (European alt) →</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Liebherr wine cooler repair — frequently asked</h2>
    {faqs.map(f => (<details class="faq"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p set:html={f.a}></p></details>))}
  </div></section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Liebherr wine cooler down? Call the branch closest to your home.</h2>
    <p>Same-day appliance repair across Los Angeles, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside counties. Residential diagnostic $89, waived with repair.</p>
  </div></section>
  <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="float-call" aria-label="Call now">☎ Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root { --red: #C8102E; --black: #0a0a0a; --gray: #f5f5f5; --border: #e2e2e2; --text: #1a1a1a; --muted: #6b6b6b; }
  body { color: var(--text); } .wrap { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; } .wrap.narrow { max-width: 820px; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; line-height: 1.15; margin: 12px 0 20px; color: var(--black); }
  h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--black); }
  h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0 0 10px; color: var(--black); }
  h4 { font-size: 1.02rem; margin: 0 0 6px; color: var(--black); }
  p { line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .call-banner { background: var(--red); color: #fff; padding: 10px 0; }
  .call-banner .wrap { display:flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .call-banner .phone-lg { color:#fff; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .hero { background: var(--black); color: #fff; padding: 42px 0 56px; } .hero h1 { color: #fff; }
  .hero .lede { font-size: 1.06rem; color: #d7d7d7; max-width: 680px; }
  .hero .crumb { color: #9a9a9a; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 6px; } .hero .crumb a { color: #c9c9c9; text-decoration: none; }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 18px 0 24px; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--red); color: #fff; } .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #fff; }
  .hero-facts { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; color: #c9c9c9; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .hero-facts li { padding: 6px 0; border-top: 1px solid #222; } .hero-facts li:first-child { border-top: 0; }
  .trust-bar { background: var(--red); color: #fff; padding: 14px 0; }
  .trust-bar .wrap { display: flex; gap: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .section { padding: 56px 0; } .section.alt { background: var(--gray); }
  .fail-block { background: #fff; border-left: 3px solid var(--red); padding: 20px 22px; margin: 16px 0; }
  .price-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 14px; background: #fff; }
  .price-table th, .price-table td { text-align: left; padding: 11px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .price-table th { background: var(--black); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .small { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-top: 12px; }
  .area-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 18px; }
  .area-grid > div { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; }
  .related-links { list-style: none; padding: 0; } .related-links li { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .related-links a { color: var(--red); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; } .related-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .faq { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .faq summary { font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px 0; } .faq p { margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .cta-bottom { background: var(--black); color: #fff; padding: 48px 0; } .cta-bottom h2 { color: #fff; } .cta-bottom p { color: #c9c9c9; }
  .float-call { position: fixed; bottom: 18px; right: 18px; background: var(--red); color: #fff; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.28); z-index: 50; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  @media (max-width: 820px) { h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; } h2 { font-size: 1.45rem; } .float-call { padding: 11px 14px; font-size: 0.88rem; } .trust-bar .wrap { gap: 14px; font-size: 0.85rem; } }
</style>
